headline.main: AXIS IS CAUTIOUS ON LIBYA FIGHTING; Decisive Stage Not Reached, Berlin Says -- Rome Claims Land and Air Gains

lead_paragraph: BERLIN, Nov. 23 (AP) -- The German High Command said today that Axis armies were stemming the great British offensive in Libya in "successful battles" featured by violent tank and air clashes and enormous destruction of war materials.
